{"tid":882824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"00後係咪覺得金庸小說=文言文？","createTime":"2018-10-30T11:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T11:36:22.000Z","uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a529d88b41d0602fe67b8875b0a19c991b8f6160","tid":882824,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;渾水<br />\n12 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n多謝你滋潤了我的初中，我第一本睇嘅係《天龍八部》，三條主角缐互相牽引，中間頑皮鬼倪匡仲要改寫過幾次，當時睇得都幾吃力。聞說呢一代嘅小朋友會覺得金庸係文言文，所以拒之千里，真係可惜。<br />\n呢個星期香港文壇爆發所謂嘅罵戰，針對着西西的《我城》，最後發展成泥漿摔角，食花生嘅人沒有任何知性得益，甚為可惜。唔知道文壇討論可唔可以真係撥亂反正，重新研究將品味帶入生活。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e4b9b79d3b0d49acd2002bb3cd93dcec117309","tid":882824,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"佢好似支持六四屠城"},{"pid":"ba83ba35bb4eb4f32706b0554054d0972ead6bf7","tid":882824,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14e4b9b79d3b0d49acd2002bb3cd93dcec117309","tid":882824,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"佢好似支持六四屠城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6296cc70c08be387408b3fa0b15cb0cb3a9a8f23","tid":882824,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"😂😂"}]}